717957f-a.text:
213 and 223-229 Ave. C, west side, north from East 13th to 14th Streets, showing a garage and a Vacant lot where three 5-story tenements (Nos. 215 to 219) stood. The large 6-story apartment house (No. 223.229)
also bears Nos. 644-652 East 14th Street.
June 1, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.

711162f-a.text:
East 13th St., adjoining the S. W. corner of Ave. C., showing a vacant lot at that location. The photographer is viewing southward on same to show on the left the rears of building on the west side of Ave. C.
March 4, 1938.
P.L. Sperr.
